text: Payette County is a county which is found in the state of Idaho in the United States of America. As of the 2020 census, 25,386 people lived there.The county seat and largest city is Payette. == Communities == === Cities === * Fruitland * New Plymouth * Payette === Unincorporated community === * Hamilton Corner == References == Category:1910s establishments in Idaho Category:1917 establishments in the United States Category:Idaho counties
